Hi!

###########

<Commands>:

	``/nick  <display_name>``       : change your display name
	``/me <action>``                : send the action you are doing. /me will be replaced by your display name
	``/join <room_alias>``          : join a room
	``/leave <user_id>``            : leave current room
	``/kick <user_id> [<reason>]``  : kick the user
	``/ban <user_id> [<reason>] ``  : ban the user
	``/unban <user_id>``            : unban the user
	``/op <user_id> <power_level>`` : set user power level
	``/deop <user_id>``             : reset user power level to the room default value

	``!help`` : this help
	``!clear``: clear timeline

#####################

<Keyboard shortcuts>:

	"M" is "Modifier" (see first item in SETTINGS["ui"]["key-modifier"]). You are you. Let's go!
	
	M-1, M-2, ..., M-9 : switching to opened room №1, №2, ..., №9 or to last opened room
	M-Tab       : autocompleting names of members
	M-Backspace : standard behavior ;)
	M-Enter     : sending message
	M-n         : creating new screen
	M-t         : put focus in title (if not focus in message buffer!)
	M-i         : put focus in infobar (if not focus in message buffer!)
	M-<         : switching to previous room (if not focus in message buffer!)
	M->         : switching to next room (if not focus in message buffer!)
	M-e         : switching to message buffer
